text.so: Sida qaalibka ah wuxuu ku noolyahay Digaale
Aafo dabiicaya ama aafo samays ah
Ceel daboolan/ Ceel biyood dusha ka dedan
Ceel biyood dusha ka furan oon wax daboola lahayn
Biyo dhulka ka soo baxaya oo daboolan
Biyo dhulka ka soo baxaya oo aan daboolnayn
Booyad yar ama gaadhi biyo lagu soo qaato si ku meelgaadh ah
Biyo dhulka dushiisa ah/Wabi/balay/ Haro/ dhijaan/Doox
Sam gaas/ gaasta wax lagu karsado
Gaas dabiici ah/ Qaas laga diyaariyey qashinka
meelkale oo guriga ka tirsan ayaa lagu hayaa
tubaakada noocyada kala duwan sida sigaarka, badeecada iyo buuriga

text.en: I don't have a phone number
A household member is usually present during data collection hours (workdays 8AM to 4PM)
text.so: Masuulku waxa uu guriga ka maqna kaliya markii laga qadayey xogta

text.en: A household member is usually only present outside of data collection hours (workdays 8AM to 4PM)
text.so: Masuulku waxa uu guriga  joogay xiligii xogta la qaadayey oo kaliya

text.en: Shelter has been vacated for a long time
text.so: Gurigan waxa laga maqnaa mudo dheer
Dadkii guriga deganaa way ka safreen

queries.selection: household_id = ? AND member_status = ? AND age_years < ? AND vaccine_consent = ?
queries.newRowInitialElementKeyToValueMap: {household_id: data('household_id'), participant_id: (() => { var count = data('membercount'); count = count + 1; assign('membercount', count); var result = data('household_id') + '' + (count < 10 ? '0'+count : count); return result; })(), member_status: 0}
